show.description: Jab ek perfect-looking couple ke peeche chhupi ho itni dark reality, toh har rishta, har sach jhooth lagne lagta hai. Sofia aur Lumor ki kahani sirf pyaar nahi, revenge, manipulation aur betrayal se bhari ek psychological thriller hai. To dekhiye  ye intense kahani jahan har character ke paas hai ek khaufnaak raaz.
